title: I Don't Know My Name
lyrics: I don't know my name And I don't play by the rules of the game So you said I'm just trying Just trying So I heard you are my sisters friend You get along quite nicely You ask me why I cut my hair And change myself completely I don't know my name I don't play by the rules of the game So you said I'm just trying Just trying I am lost Trying to get found In an ocean of people I don't know my name I don't play by the rules of the game So you said I'm just trying Just trying I now know my name I don't play by the rules of the game So you said I'm not trying But I'm trying To find my way
